rishav.message: Hey! Ready to start the game?
Put the red apple on the red square mat
Put the yellow apple on the circle mat
Put the whole bread on the green square mat at the left bottom of the table
Put the whole bread on the green square mat at the left middle centre of the table
Put the only vase on the violet mat
Put the only egg on the iris mat
Congratulations. We are done with the game. Thanks for playing
